content: I think Estes Park sounds like a great option. I've heard great things about Rocky Mountain National Park. Can you give me more information about the cabins you found in Estes Park? Are they close to the national park, and do they have any other amenities like a full kitchen or BBQ grill? By the way, my brother got car sick on the way to the beach house today, and we had to pull over twice for him to throw up.
